  "text": "Clinical studies in patients with HBV/HIV coinfection reported lower response rates to standard IFN-␣ treatment than those with HBV monoinfection. [CITATION_1] Responders tend to have a higher mean CD4 cell count than nonresponders. It is expected that pegIFN-␣ will have similar or better efficacy than standard IFN-␣.",
